From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 10:11:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Stage 1 (MVP): scaffold LeetCode study tracker

Vite + React + TS + Tailwind app with local-first architecture:
- Dexie (IndexedDB) cache with background Supabase sync (last-write-wins)
- Single-account auto sign-in (no login UI); RLS preserved
- Problem CRUD with filter/search/sort, detail view, create/edit form
- Dashboard: totals, difficulty/tag progress, study streak
- JSON export/import backup
- supabase/schema.sql with problems + review_logs + RLS policies

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01JJ2ALpPXcgcr9CfdzcsDU4
